Fig. 70
). Anal lobe with complete fringe of about 20–22 Taeniae and 2 dorsal taeniae on each side. Segments II–IV with 3 L setae; segment V–VI with 3 taeniae; segment VII with 4 taeniae; segment VIII with 5 taeniae.

